OL,3,CProposal for law supporting parents of
OL,4,Ccritically ill children blocked by
OL,5,CLabour
OL,7,FA law proposed to give parents of
OL,8,Fcritically ill children workplace
OL,9,Frights and financial support has been
OL,10,Fblocked by Labour in the House of
OL,11,FLords.
OL,13,FUnder current law, parents of newborn
OL,14,Fbabies who become unwell within the
OL,15,Ffirst 28 days of life are entitled to
OL,16,Fpaid leave and job protection to be by
OL,17,Ftheir child's bedside.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
