OL,4,Ccritically ill children blocked by
OL,5,CLabour
OL,7,FBut if their child is diagnosed with
OL,8,Fcancer at 29 days old, the parents no
OL,9,Flonger have the right to financial
OL,10,Fsupport.
OL,12,FCeri and Frances Menai-Davis, who lost
OL,13,Ftheir young son to cancer, are
OL,14,Fcampaigning for the government to
OL,15,Fbring in Hugh's Law, which would give
OL,16,Fparents statutory rights if their
OL,17,Fchild is critically ill.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
