OL,7,FAsking for an explanation, Ulster
OL,8,FUnionist MP Robin Swann said
OL,9,FEmployment Rights Minister Justin
OL,10,FMadders MP had "turned his back" on
OL,11,Fthe parents.
OL,13,FResponding, the minister said: "We're
OL,14,Fnot turning our back on parents or
OL,15,Fchildren. We're actually having the
OL,16,Fbiggest expansion in workers' rights
OL,17,Fand family-friendly policies that
OL,18,Fwe've seen in a generation.
