OL,7,F"Clearly, we're not going to be able
OL,8,Fto satisfy every issue in this area.
OL,9,FBut that's the point of this review.
OL,10,FWe're looking at the system in the
OL,11,Fround. It needs improving, needs
OL,12,Fmodernising. And that's what we intend
OL,13,Fto do."
OL,15,FWhy did Labour block Hugh's Law?
OL,16,FMinister Justin Madders MP responds
OL,18,FCeri said it was "deeply
OL,19,Fdisappointing" to see Labour reject
OL,20,Fthe proposals, given they appear to
OL,21,Fhave cross party support.
