OL,7,F"And we realised at that point there
OL,8,Fis nothing in place in the UK that
OL,9,Fprovides support, financial support to
OL,10,Fparents of a sick child."
OL,12,FAt present, parents of critically ill
OL,13,Fchildren must rely on unpaid Carer's
OL,14,FLeave, which is capped at just one
OL,15,Fweek per year. Disability living
OL,16,Fallowance is available to claim on
OL,17,Fbehalf of the child, but parents must
OL,18,Fwait 90 days before applying and an
OL,19,Fapplication can take up to 20 weeks to
OL,20,Fbe processed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
